This parameter is required.', example='test-etljob'),
  project?: string(name='project', description='The destination Project name.

This parameter is required.', example='test-project'),
  roleArn?: string(name='roleArn', description='The role ARN used to write to the destination Logstore.

This parameter is required.', example='acs:ram::13234:role/logtarget'),
